oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: I Will Always Love You Quote
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Quotations; Woodcuts (prints);
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (green and red on blue) that reads "I will always love you, he said., and she said hoe do you know? I just know he said. And then she remembered that one of the things she loved about him was that he knew so much." Poster features a woodcut of a heart.
